;     MAY 1,2014,JOR, LEG RENAMED STATS FOR CONSISTENCY WITH PLT_HIST2D AND OLDER PROS
;                     LEG IS RESERVED FOR LEGEND IN FUTURE VERSIONS
;     JUL 3,2014,JOR REVISED KEYWORD INPUTS TO PLT_XY
